description:
Made in collaboration with artist Tyler Hackett, this jersey has a visual that will catch the eye of lovers of freshwater shark fishing, the pike!

Maded with a high quality fabric made of 100% organic cotton, which allows it to keep a pleasant texture and optimal comfort. Its regular cut will allow you superior comfort during your outdoor activities while its sublime printed logo and its contrasting sleeves and collar will give you an unparalleled look in your daily life.
name: Hooke Gone Fishing Tee - Mens
